  "decision_conditions": [
    "REASON: The proposed roof extension by reason of its inappropriate design, scale and massing would represent an unsightly interruption to the unaltered and uniform roof forms along 1-17 Wharfdale Road  and would fail to respect the significance of the designated asset.  The development is considered to have a detrimental impact on the established character and appearance of the original building and the terrace to which it forms part. The proposal is contrary to policy 9 of Islington’s Core strategy 2011,  policies D4 (Designing in context), D11 (Alterations and extensions), D25 (Roof extensions)  of the Islington Unitary Development Plan 2002,  Islington’s Urban Design Guide 2006, Keystone Crescent conservation guidance note and PPS 5."
